{"tid":814740,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"時空幻境系列 新作 Tales of Crestoria","createTime":"2018-09-11T12:38:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-12T11:11:56.000Z","uid":194281,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"4c20907b64410676dc6dd8d5ec79e68f0f5bfcd5","tid":814740,"uid":194281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T12:38:30.000Z","msg":"萬代南夢宮於今（11）日宣布，旗下知名 RPG 系列《時空幻境（Tales of）》系列的最新作《Tales of Crestoria（テイルズ オブ クレストリア）》即將於智慧型手機平台（iOS / Android）上推出。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根據官方所公布的資訊，本作是完全原創的新作，由田川智美擔任製作人。以「從智慧型手機開始的全新《傳奇》」為標語，即日起開始事前登錄，屆時將採免費下載、道具付費制。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本作以「罪」為主題，描述了主角背負著罪過、為了自己重視的事物而活下去的故事。目前三名角色的預告插圖已經釋出，之後將會陸續公開詳細情報。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在官方網站上，也已經開放了由中田康貴（中田ヤスタカ）與神風動畫聯手打造的概念影片，影片中可以看到手上有印記的主角抓緊燃起火焰的大劍瞪視前方。而在另一隻以主角視點呈現的「another ver.」概念影片中，出現在主角面前的人物又究竟是⋯⋯？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/11/203807_b934cb9e50d9d985382bc622b7bbfc1e.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F11%2F203807_b934cb9e50d9d985382bc622b7bbfc1e.JPG&h=c4c487bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/11/203810_b83019f316310438c7960661ddf474b9.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F11%2F203810_b83019f316310438c7960661ddf474b9.JPG&h=cea93c0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/11/203815_fa97b0429515b165a2e0645e55e304cd.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F11%2F203815_fa97b0429515b165a2e0645e55e304cd.JPG&h=623ed46e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又一個系列收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afae0521b263cc0c2246db1cd7a3e94cec8ac94f","tid":814740,"uid":194281,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T12:40:58